 * Video Unwraping
   [ ] Support 360 vídeos and unwrap frame by frame into a final rectangular 
	video.
   [ ] Allow generating equirectangular videos.

Version 0.3
~~~~~~~~~~~

 * Viewer
   [ ] Viewer of unwrapped images.
   [ ] Support multiple projections: planar, cube, cilinder, sphere.

Version 0.2
