 * Image Unwrapping
   [ ] Suport equirectangular image output.
 * Settings
   [ ] Configure color to fill blank spots in equirectangular outputs.

Version 0.1
~~~~~~~~~~~

 * Image Unwrapping
   [x] Unwrap 360 degree images into rectangular images of several sizes.
   [x] Allow the usual interpolations: neirest neighbor, bilinear, and bicubic.
   [x] Save resulting image.
 * Settings   
   [x] Vertical FOV
   [x] Final image size
   [x] Scaling algorithm
